  <name>System Monitor</name>
  <summary>A highly configurable system resource monitor for the COSMIC DE</summary>
  <description>
    <p>A highly configurable system resource monitor applet for the COSMIC desktop environment. Customize everything from the visual theme and layout of components to paddings and sampling rates. Supports vertical bar charts, run charts, and a minimalist design for seamless panel integration.</p>
    <p>Monitors a variety of system resources:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>CPU usage (global and per core)</li>
      <li>Memory usage (RAM and Swap)</li>
      <li>Network I/O</li>
      <li>Disk I/O</li>
      <li>GPU (usage and VRAM)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
